'''''Animals Are Beautiful People''''' (nanone yitwa '''''Beautiful People''''') ni documentaire y’ibidukikije yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo yo mu 1974 yanditswe, yakozwe, iyoborwa, ifatwa amashusho kandi ihindurwa na Jamie Uys, ivuga ku nyamaswa zo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika yepfo]], zerekanwe nibintu bisetsa. Yafatiwe amashusho mu butayu bwa Namib, ubutayu bwa Kalahari n'umugezi wa Okavango na Delta ya Okavango .. yahawe igihembo cya Golden Globe 1974 muri Filime Nziza . 

Iyi filime, intsinzi ikomeye mu bucuruzi, yakozwe mu bwigenge na Uys, izwi kandi nyuma yo gusetsa  muri  ''[[The Gods Must Be Crazy]]'' (1980).

